Package: teleport-route-checker
Version: 1.0.0
Section: net
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: systemd, iproute2, gawk
Maintainer: Will Shih <will@example.com>
Description: Automatic route management for Teleport interfaces
 This package provides a systemd service that automatically manages
 network routes for Teleport (tlprtX) interfaces on UniFi gateways.
 .
 It monitors for new Teleport connections and adds appropriate routes
 to ensure proper connectivity for devices connecting via Teleport.
